Description:
    scaffold, migration and locale

Example:
    rails generate gallifrey_scaffold model attribute:type attribute:type ...
    rails generate gallifrey scaffold price:price name:string visible:boolean description:richtext
    rails generate gallifrey_scaffold product family:references price:price name:string visible:boolean description:richtext
    
    rails generate gallifrey_migration AddColorToProducts color:string

    rails generate gallifrey_locale {fr|en|all}

    rails generate gallifrey_jointable product tag

    rails generate gallifrey_devisecancan user
       
